{"tid":2456061,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方稱5名警員曾接觸確診巴基斯坦籍男子　須接受檢疫","createTime":"2021-03-21T15:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T16:56:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"30e1681482a434d7f01bf540969319ab76d958d1","tid":2456061,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:22:36.000Z","msg":"本港新增8宗新型肺炎確診，4宗屬本地感染，當中1宗源頭不明，患者是早前涉嫌非法集結被捕的巴基斯坦籍男子。警方表示，有5名曾接觸被捕男子的警員列為密切接觸者，已經接受隔離檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，已安排曾接觸被捕男子的15名警員接受病毒檢測，全部初步結果呈陰性，當中5名警員屬緊密接觸者。警方又表示，相關警員工作期間有佩戴口罩，其後沒有與公眾接觸，警方已派員清潔及消毒觀塘警署及警車等地方。<br />\n<br />\n有關案件發生於本月19日晚上，警方接報指油塘三家村遊樂場附近有多人聚集，東九龍衝鋒隊及觀塘警區反三合會行動組人員接報到場後，拘捕9名本地男子及8名非華裔男子，年齡介乎13歲至36歲，涉嫌非法集結，所有被捕人士已獲准保釋候查，確診男子被捕後報稱不適，送往聯合醫院，星期日確診。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581768-20210321.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581768-20210321.htm&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=76912e86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581768-20210321.htm&h=6cc433a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581768-20210321.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1ad02bef55c9221372a4628a11503c5dd7770a37","tid":2456061,"uid":52779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7e3a09032e57f75dec0a4a879c67c5f38576c2","tid":2456061,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T15:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c769c34123df05b84c44fe8fadc52c448b5bd3","tid":2456061,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2f973969bf2aee6361946b7bb6b3efb934a52d","tid":2456061,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}